text: Rodney Govinden (born September 13, 1984) is a Seychellois sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's Laser event, in which he placed 45th. He was the flag bearer for Seychells at the 2016 Summer Olympics Parade of Nations. He has qualified to represent Seychelles at the 2020 Summer Olympics in the men's Laser event. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Seychellois male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Seychelles Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:African Games bronze medalists for Seychelles Category:African Games medalists in sailing Category:Competitors at the 2011 All-Africa Games
